		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">WedNESday wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">IMO Nestopia is better. Apart from WedNESday, it is the only emulator can run 10 Yard Fight properly.</div>
<br />
<br />That's probably because your ROM image has incorrect mirroring selected and Nestopia is using its internal database to correct it.
<br />Try switching it to Horizontal mirroring and you'll probably find that it works just fine in every other emulator.

		

		</td>
